#Topic for today - 

Using ChatGPT Go to create a bio for yourself.

#Prompt for the day - 

Ask me a series of questions to understand my skills, experience, interests, achievements, knowledge areas, and what I want to be known for professionally. 

Ask the questions one at a time and wait for my response before asking the next question. 

After collecting enough information, create three things based on my answers: 
1) a professional LinkedIn bio
2) a short and engaging Instagram bio
3) a single powerful one line statement that I can use in my resume to describe myself. 

Ensure the writing is clear, concise, and highlights my strengths.

